#
# Wave 349 theme: SafeUUID enum members are instances of SafeUUID.
#
# SafeUUID.safe.__class__.__name__ == 'SafeUUID' (8 chars; the member's own class).
# SafeUUID.unsafe.__class__.__name__ == 'SafeUUID' (8 chars; same class).
# SafeUUID.__name__.__eq__('SafeUUID') (confirmed).
# SafeUUID.__module__.__eq__('uuid') (confirmed).
# No prior uuid spec anchors SafeUUID member class names as a table under uuidsafe159.
# Verified Python 3.14.3 macOS/Darwin 25.4.0.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

